    {"type":"text","id":"d5_left_d","x":120,"y":2690,"width":380,"height":210,"text":"Pre-indexed documents in Milvus\n\n1. Embed query (Gemini 3072-dim)\n2. COSINE similarity search\n3. Top-K chunks returned\n4. Visual fallback via screenshots\n\nBest for:\n  Specific factual questions\n  Known document collections\n  Fast sub-second retrieval","originalText":"Pre-indexed documents in Milvus\n\n1. Embed query (Gemini 3072-dim)\n2. COSINE similarity search\n3. Top-K chunks returned\n4. Visual fallback via screenshots\n\nBest for:\n  Specific factual questions\n  Known document collections\n  Fast sub-second retrieval","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#374151","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":150009,"version":1,"versionNonce":150010,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},

